slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:43:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ec1a63a769ac72373bcaf02f66cb8f23504e7e2","tid":1205200,"uid":82521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0ded2666a9cacaa5cb8d2802e6f48aa26ca1348","tid":1205200,"uid":62881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:44:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"057a68a4a81f720494416bc00c0057b867707e41","tid":1205200,"uid":62881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"154ebefd9af2fc41279ed4d8fd9930c8938b0317","tid":1205200,"uid":62881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cf90bdacbae94d02b8be61957c4e71274aa89c5","tid":1205200,"uid":82521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"107f404715e34f00c70f04749bacf84f9b53a7f9","tid":1205200,"uid":82521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:57:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59996c7118ef55929d8700a600957cf404fcf398","tid":1205200,"uid":62881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9ab4dda3d8aea335bf0638a1a54ff327c8d4db4b","tid":1205200,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:08:45.000Z","msg":"唔係重點，但大家有緣見到CCTVB做直播/收音就大嗌或自製banner<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嗌咩唔係重點，齊心屌鳩☭☭TVB☭☭<br />\n目的係影響☭☭tvb☭☭收音，拍攝緊嘅畫面<br />\n過往經驗，佢做live無得cut，直上電視，但新聞時段就會cut晒呢啲畫面/收音，令佢無嘢播都好<br />\n<br />\n橫掂☭☭TVB☭☭妓者都係鳩噏<br />\n血債血償，清鳩☭☭tvb☭☭袋<br />\n<br />\n有片，例子參考 : <br />\n[呼籲]有緣見到CCTVB，大家要識做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1202083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202083</a>"},{"pid":"fbf5aec6a57317b9d4015dbab4afe729720eeaf2","tid":1205200,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s